# Stow ignore for the `agents` package.
# NOTE: providing this file REPLACES stow's built-in default ignore list,
# so the defaults are reproduced below, then our package-specific additions.

# --- stow built-in defaults (keep in sync with `info stow 'Types And Syntax Of Ignore Lists'`) ---
RCS
.+,v
CVS
\.\#.+
\.cvsignore
\.svn
_darcs
\.hg
\.git
\.gitignore
\.gitmodules
.+~
\#.*\#
^/README.*
^/LICENSE.*
^/COPYING

# --- package-specific ---
# Claude Desktop rewrites this file at runtime (device name, account UUID,
# epitaxyPrefs, sidebarMode). Symlinking it would either clobber live state or
# pump runtime churn back into the repo. We keep the committed copy as a seed
# reference but do NOT stow it; the live ~/Library copy is left untouched.
claude_desktop_config\.json
